# Keep Vercel uploads small and under the free-tier 5000-file limit.
# vercel-rust compiles from source on Vercel, so none of these belong in the
# upload. (A deploy without an effective ignore tried to push 2.6GB — target/,
# .git, and a .claude/ agent worktree — which blew past the 5000-file cap and
# triggered a 24h upload rate-limit.)
target
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
.claude
.vercel
*.log
